TITLE: Episode 47 - DLive, Biased Machine Learning Models, Quantum Computing, and Starlink
DESCRIPTION: This week, Thaddeus and Gary talk about DLive, the blockchain-based livestreaming alternative to YouTube and Twitch. They also discuss the pitfalls of building woke AI, the burgeoning quantum computing race, and the continung rollout of Starlink.
